{"tid":1791631,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港豬：「匯豐咁做係正常程序喎，佢都唔想架，砌佢既意義係咩呢？」","createTime":"2019-12-21T04:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T16:36:21.000Z","uid":100155,"like":38,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5814e12aa3471fb036775add962bd9f414e1068e","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">指名制裁匯豐高層係要阻嚇企業繼續向中共獻媚打壓香港抗爭者</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個月前, 港澳辦主任會見匯豐幾位高層，包括行政總裁王冬勝，同期星火戶口被警告及關閉。<br />\n<br />\n一個月後，星火戶口被指洗黑錢，星火被人拉埋。匯豐高層（包括CE王冬勝 Peter Wong）以政治命令ban左星火戶口<br />\n事前事後仲見埋港澳辦主任<br />\n咁鍾意賣港 全香港人都唔會忘記你架。                                   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tasdq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tasdq1.jpg&h=5ac0f74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAowcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAowcH.jpg&h=df780bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eetdTrc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeetdTrc.png&h=c40e01c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>咁鍾意賣港 全香港人都唔會忘記你架。</strong></span>     <br />\n<br />\n原news<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/en/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00005/NOW.977508/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Fen%2Fstocks%2Fanalysis%2Fstock-aafn-content%2F00005%2FNOW.977508%2Fall&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=826f7a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/en/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00005/NOW.977508/all</a><br />\n===================================<br />\n<br />\n「匯豐咁做係正常程序喎，佢都唔想架」：<br />\n<br />\n開空殻公司從來都係好多公司/組織/NGO既正常操作，如果要查，大量戶口都會同「開戶時所陳述的用途不相符」，如果係決定要針對呢一個戶口然後話只係「正常運作」，HSBC只係當緊包括香港同美國在內既全世界用緊銀行服務既人係傻仔。<br />\n<br />\n多cash transaction就係洗黑錢，唱錢店（msb)同賭場係咪要全部違反aml，但點解有得做edd而唔係即刻報jfiu同凍結呢？而星火就封得咁急？<br />\n<br />\n有做bank都知大把mainland account都係鬼，點解又唔理/只rfi/periodic/EDD呢？點解星火又無呢d、仲要一個月內close account呢？咁樣close account係咪global standard?<br />\n<br />\n要棄明投暗，冇人阻止到；服務緊咩野人，放棄咩野人，全世界人都看在眼內；唔好侮辱人類既智慧，唔好以為可以永遠食兩家茶禮。"},{"pid":"4f4aff83c92237c2f8236ac6bc69e28c83154a54","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"陳健波間許氏找換，到今時今日都仲生勾勾，點解星火就封，許氏就無事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191125/60298512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191125%2F60298512&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=5ae786a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191125%2F60298512&h=3b0b6dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191125/60298512</a>"},{"pid":"10c5dbd96d248794ddba5a5b82a3ae5761b36d38","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"點解匯豐唔停埋中聯辦同中國外交部駐港旗下公司的洗黑錢行為？"},{"pid":"345c25e59d046294a2c672094a6c4dc2f3a753d5","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"中國官員億億入錢香港買地買樓買保險就無問題，港人捐錢比個legal aid funds就係要close account？"},{"pid":"26062f1b9c5a740118a9d0c0f0a8506668393190","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"張崑陽：聲援星火集會 尋求國際援助 下星期一遮打見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPOUCVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPOUCVH.png&h=5e0ea5bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"136829e24ab733ff4956bcd38f5f6e1bdc56f3e7","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"