,{"pid":"a817445d3c5230694bfcc6af1f39839331f14538","tid":1791631,"uid":31765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"HSBC 都close左好多大陸account, 只不過無報出黎，或者無咁大迴響。<br />\n<br />\n調轉係任何一間香港營業既銀行，結果都會係一樣，我相信就算星火個account去左citibank到開，結果都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n你地成日倒果為因，諗下真正敵人係邊個啦！"},{"pid":"84c38c6eb704f72d491c6e21feee1eb021c040bd","tid":1791631,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"daaea4b504cc1b39401410e96519d4dd401e67a2","tid":1791631,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"打啦打啦打走哂佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905993264c091390dd3687aafb370a9c14ac56a2","tid":1791631,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5814e12aa3471fb036775add962bd9f414e1068e","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">指名制裁匯豐高層係要阻嚇企業繼續向中共獻媚打壓香港抗爭者</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個月前, 港澳辦主任會見匯豐幾位高層，包括行政總裁王冬勝，同期星火戶口被警告及關閉。<br />\n<br />\n一個月後，星火戶口被指洗黑錢，星火被人拉埋。匯豐高層（包括CE王冬勝 Peter Wong）以政治命令ban左星火戶口<br />\n事前事後仲見埋港澳辦主任<br />\n咁鍾意賣港 全香港人都唔會忘記你架。                                   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tasdq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tasdq1.jpg&h=5ac0f74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAowcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAowcH.jpg&h=df780bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eetdTrc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeetdTrc.png&h=c40e01c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>咁鍾意賣港 全香港人都唔會忘記你架。</strong></span>     <br />\n<br />\n原news<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/en/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00005/NOW.977508/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Fen%2Fstocks%2Fanalysis%2Fstock-aafn-content%2F00005%2FNOW.977508%2Fall&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=826f7a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/en/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00005/NOW.977508/all</a><br />\n===================================<br />\n<br />\n「匯豐咁做係正常程序喎，佢都唔想架」：<br />\n<br />\n開空殻公司從來都係好多公司/組織/NGO既正常操作，如果要查，大量戶口都會同「開戶時所陳述的用途不相符」，如果係決定要針對呢一個戶口然後話只係「正常運作」，HSBC只係當緊包括香港同美國在內既全世界用緊銀行服務既人係傻仔。<br />\n<br />\n多cash transaction就係洗黑錢，唱錢店（msb)同賭場係咪要全部違反aml，但點解有得做edd而唔係即刻報jfiu同凍結呢？而星火就封得咁急？<br />\n<br />\n有做bank都知大把mainland account都係鬼，點解又唔理/只rfi/periodic/EDD呢？點解星火又無呢d、仲要一個月內close account呢？咁樣close account係咪global standard?<br />\n<br />\n要棄明投暗，冇人阻止到；服務緊咩野人，放棄咩野人，全世界人都看在眼內；唔好侮辱人類既智慧，唔好以為可以永遠食兩家茶禮。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"唔好以為撻啲terms 出嚟就有道理<br />\n<br />\n以你嘅講法，美國佬告慢慢周詐騙銀行都係冇道理啦係咪？"}],"pinned":{"pid":"10c5dbd96d248794ddba5a5b82a3ae5761b36d38","tid":1791631,"uid":100155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"點解匯豐唔停埋中聯辦同中國外交部駐港旗下公司的洗黑錢行為？"}}